  "monster": {
    "title": "Beoq.",
    "body": "One of the many lords of Pandemonium, Beoq has a skeletal body which hovers in mid-air and a cubic structure in place of a head. It is surrounded by a weird haze. It changes colour whenever you look at it.\n\n<lightgrey>Max HP: 211     </lightgrey><lightgrey> Will: ++       </lightgrey><lightgrey>   AC: +        </lightgrey><lightgrey>  EV: ++++ ++   </lightgrey>                \n<lightgrey>    rF: ++.     </lightgrey><lightgrey>   rC: ++.      </lightgrey><lightgrey>rPois: +        </lightgrey><lightgrey>rNeg: ∞         </lightgrey><darkgrey>rElec: .        </darkgrey>\n<lightgrey>Threat: Lethal  </lightgrey><lightgrey>Class: Demonic  </lightgrey><lightgrey> Size: Large    </lightgrey><lightgrey> Int: Human     </lightgrey>\nSpeed: 160%\n\nYou have about 30% to hit with the earth staff of Heof.\nIt has about 27% to hit you.\n\nAttack  Max Damage  \nHit     39          \n\nIt is immune to torment; and resistant to steam and miasma.\nIt can see invisible.\nIt can fly.\nIt can open doors.\nSPELLSET_PLACEHOLDERTo read a description, press the key listed above. (AdB) indicates damage (the sum of A B-sided dice), (x%) indicates the chance to defeat your Will, and (y) indicates the spell range; shown in red if you are in range.\n\nIt is currently targeting Beoq.\n\nThis monster has been temporarily summoned to this location. If angered it will immediately vanish, yielding no experience or items; it is incapable of using stairs.",
    "quote": "",
    "status": "<white>Lightly drained:<lightgrey>\n   This creature has been lightly drained, somewhat lowering the accuracy of\n   their melee attacks, the power of their spells and special attack properties,\n   and making them slightly more vulnerable to many status effects.\n\n",
